<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You will miss out massively if you read the abridged version. The Count of Monte Cristo has a million subplots, the most intricate character relations<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You will miss out massively if you read the abridged version. The Count of Monte Cristo has a million subplots, the most intricate character relationships and conflicts.<br />Reading the abridged version of any book is like eating the microwavable version of any meal. Absolutely get the full version.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
