  <span id="freeText701292678260436880" style="display:none">Revenge is a dish best served cold. And unabridged. And translated from the French by Robin Buss.<br><br>The greatness of this book can be illustrated by the following simple equations:<br><br>(<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/7326750@N03/4924318270/" title="count-von-count-sesame-street by woemcats, on Flickr" rel="nofollow noopener">
